dev/notes/phase9-handoff.md:19:- **Lifecycle observability surface is matrix-bound.** Phase enum has exactly five values. EventSource has exactly two. EventCategory has seven. CounterSnapshot has seven keys. Adding a new Event field, new Phase variant, new EventSource, new EventCategory, or new CounterSnapshot key requires a successor ADR + interface-doc update in the same PR. Do NOT silently extend.
